    {
      "span_id": "p051_s0001",
      "text": "INCITS xxx-200x Link Services Rev 1.61 November 3, 2006",
      "bbox": [
        301.08,
        37.27,
        539.95,
        47.32
      ],
      "block_index": 1,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p051_s0002",
      "text": " 32",
      "bbox": [
        521.04,
        723.59,
        534.92,
        734.7
      ],
      "block_index": 2,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p051_s0003",
      "text": "In order to direct the RCS ELS Request frame to the Fabric, an Nx_Port specifies the D_ID as the",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        57.65,
        539.97,
        68.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p051_s0004",
      "text": "Fabric Controller (i.e., FFFFFDh).",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        69.65,
        244.27,
        80.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p051_s0005",
      "text": "4.2.9.2  Protocol",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        94.97,
        172.6,
        106.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p051_s0006",
      "text": "a) Read Connection Status Request Sequence",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        118.97,
        318.47,
        130.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p051_s0007",
      "text": "b) LS_ACC or LS_RJT Reply Sequence",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        142.96,
        287.89,
        154.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p051_s0008",
      "text": "4.2.9.3  Request Sequence",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        166.96,
        221.54,
        178.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p051_s0009",
      "text": "Addressing: ",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        190.96,
        157.1,
        202.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p051_s0010",
      "text": "The S_ID field designates the source Nx_Port requesting Connection status.  The D_ID",
      "bbox": [
        157.08,
        190.96,
        539.98,
        202.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 2
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p051_s0011",
      "text": "field is the Fabric Controller, (FFFFFDh).",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        202.96,
        275.93,
        214.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p051_s0012",
      "text": "Payload: ",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        226.96,
        140.41,
        238.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p051_s0013",
      "text": "The format of the Payload is shown in table 14.  The first word of the Payload shall contain",
      "bbox": [
        140.4,
        226.96,
        539.99,
        238.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 2
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p051_s0014",
      "text": "the ELS_Command code.  The second word shall contain the N_Port_ID for which Connection status",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        238.96,
        540.05,
        250.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p051_s0015",
      "text": "is being requested.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        250.96,
        180.41,
        262.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p051_s0016",
      "text": "4.2.9.4  Reply Sequence",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        370.96,
        209.29,
        382.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p051_s0017",
      "text": "LS_RJT: ",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        394.96,
        138.19,
        406.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p051_s0018",
      "text": "LS_RJT signifies rejection of the RCS command.",
      "bbox": [
        138.18,
        394.96,
        354.77,
        406.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 2
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p051_s0019",
      "text": "LS_ACC: ",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        418.96,
        142.05,
        430.08
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p051_s0020",
      "text": "LS_ACC signifies that the Fabric has completed the request.  The format of the LS_ACC",
      "bbox": [
        142.08,
        418.96,
        539.95,
        430.08
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 2
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p051_s0021",
      "text": "Payload is shown in table 15.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        430.96,
        225.44,
        442.08
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p051_s0022",
      "text": "The Connection Status Codes are defined in table 16.",
